# Developer Operating Contract

Full policy: **`docs/DEVELOPER-OPERATING-CONTRACT.md`**

| Layer | Role |
|-------|------|
| SSOT / PHASE-5 | What is correct |
| Blueprint | What / order |
| DOC | How the agent executes |
| Local project | DB, logs, queue, tests |
| User | Biodata/GT, escalations, production approval |

**Owns the goal, not the task.** Complete only when DOC Definition of Done is fully met.

**Local-first.** Do not use live server for routine debug.

**Never ask** what local project/DB/logs/queue/git can answer.

**User instructions** (when action required): simple **Marathi (Devanagari)**, steps १–५ (कुठे, काय, किती, कधी थांबा, पुढे काय). No jargon commands for the product owner.

Report: `Complete` | `In Progress` | `Escalation` per DOC §10.
